sections.heading: to 65-4-18 - Repealed.
sections.text: Repeals.— Laws 2003, ch. 359 § 44, repealed 65-4-1 to 65-4-18 NMSA 1978, as enacted by Laws 1933, ch. 120, §§ 1 to 19, relating to motor carrier transportation agents, effective July 1, 2003. For provisions of the former sections,seethe 2002 NMSA 1978 onNMOneSource.com. For the Motor Carrier Act,see65-2A-1 NMSA 1978.
